3-a19f-feb9d3010000</link><description>美国国务卿本应亲自评估援助卡车从以色列前往加沙的通道，但由于担心抗议者出现，阻止援助卡车进入加沙，访问被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-cancels-gaza-crossing-visit-after-israel-doesnt-commit-to-stopping-aid-protests/0000018d-8a38-d443-a19f-feb9d3010000</guid></item><item><title>由于航班将返回以色列，英国航空公司最大限度地减少了运营、飞机和机组人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</link><description>在飞往以色列的途中，这架飞机将在塞浦路斯停留 45 分钟，进行机组人员换班，而乘客则留在机上。由于保险公司的条件，船员不会在以色列过夜</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</guid></item><item><title>“无处可归”：《国土报》如何讲述加沙被毁的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</link><description>“仅仅在图像旁边放置文字是不够的，”记者亚登·米凯利 (Yarden Michaeli) 谈到《国土报》对加沙地带大规模破坏的交互式视觉调查时说道。 “我们真的想让人们进入故事，以产生情感影响”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 19:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 125 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</link><description>布林肯表示，哈马斯对停火提议的回应“显然不可能”，但美国认为“这为达成协议创造了空间” ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯的答复表明总理打算在该地区寻求冲突 ■ 几名以色列人周四，一名真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩的火箭弹和导弹袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列艺术家不再是以色列艺术家时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</link><description>在本周的以色列文化综述中：艺术家兼电影制片人雅埃尔·巴塔纳 (Yael Bartana) 将代表德国参加今年的威尼斯双年展，海法取消了为两位失去亲人的父亲（一位是以色列人，另一位是巴勒斯坦人）举办的一本书的活动，特拉维夫博物馆仍在展出展览与赎罪日战争的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</guid></item><item><title>英国首相誓言打击亲巴勒斯坦集会上的“反犹太主义”和“暴力恐吓”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</link><description>英国首相谴责伦敦抗议活动中表现出的“美化恐怖主义”，并发誓在英国反犹太主义率不断上升的情况下，警方将“阻止人们遮住脸来隐瞒身份”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约一家德鲁兹餐厅的墙上挂着一面以色列国旗。这时候麻烦就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</link><description>在曼哈顿的加扎拉餐厅，老板加扎拉哈拉比自豪地认为自己是以色列人，所用的橄榄油、香草和香料都是从“家乡”带来的。 10月7日之后的尖酸刻薄、破碎的玻璃和“自由巴勒斯坦”的涂鸦让她震惊，但她无意退缩</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 16:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列撤离人员所在的酒店报告了多起性暴力和家庭暴力案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</link><description>据警方称，已立案 116 起单独档案，其中包括针对未成年人和妇女的性侵犯案件。由于持续的战争，加沙和黎巴嫩边境地区共有约20万人流离失所</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙的生活和家园被摧毁，其高等教育也被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</link><description>加沙高等教育的破坏不是“附带损害”，而是以色列摧毁物质和精神基础设施政策的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日袭击中丧生的以色列男子的家人告知加沙的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</link><description>贝埃里的梅尼·戈达尔和他的妻子在哈马斯袭击基布兹期间被杀。迄今为止，他的家人仍不知道他遗体的下落</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫居民因在公寓内刺伤妇女而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</link><description>犯罪嫌疑人是 33 岁的丹尼尔·马尔戈辛 (Daniel Margoshin)，他在夜间闯入受害人家中，刺伤她超过 31 刀。他放火烧毁了公寓和她的尸体，然后逃到耶路撒冷，在那里他试图袭击试图逮捕他的警察，结果被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</guid></item></channel></rss>